sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Insured
    participant Broker
    participant Clearance as Clearance Desk
    participant UW as Underwriter
    participant Enrich as Data Enrichment
    participant Rating as Rating Engine
    participant Referral as Referral / Authority
    participant PAS as Policy Admin System
    participant Reinsurer

    Insured->>Broker: Requests insurance
    Broker->>Broker: Prepares Acord forms,<br/>loss runs, SOV, financials
    Broker->>Clearance: Submits package
    Clearance->>Clearance: Conflict check<br/>(same account in system?)
    alt Duplicate
        Clearance-->>Broker: Decline (already working)
    else Clear
        Clearance->>UW: Routed to line underwriter
    end

    UW->>UW: Triage<br/>(appetite, size, class)
    alt Outside appetite
        UW-->>Broker: Decline
    else In appetite
        UW->>Enrich: Pull third-party data
        Enrich->>Enrich: LexisNexis, RMS,<br/>Cape Analytics, D&B,<br/>HazardHub, OFAC
        Enrich-->>UW: Enriched submission
    end

    UW->>UW: Risk assessment<br/>(hazards, controls, financials)
    UW->>Rating: Apply rating plan
    Rating-->>UW: Technical premium

    UW->>UW: Apply schedule credits/debits<br/>within authority

    alt Over authority
        UW->>Referral: Referral required
        Referral-->>UW: Approved / modified / declined
    end

    alt Large risk / capacity needed
        UW->>Reinsurer: Facultative placement
        Reinsurer-->>UW: Terms
    end

    UW->>Broker: Quote issued<br/>(premium, limits, terms)
    Broker->>Insured: Presents quote
    Insured->>Broker: Accepts
    Broker->>UW: Request to bind

    UW->>PAS: Bind the risk
    PAS->>PAS: Policy issued<br/>(declarations, forms, endorsements)
    PAS-->>Broker: Policy document
    PAS-->>Insured: Certificate / copy

    Note over UW,PAS: Insurer is on risk from bind,<br/>even before policy is issued.
